# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:60
translate portuguese u20a_531c13bb:

    # wt "She's really angry with me. Did you know she has a gang? There have been some threats."
    wt "Ela está mesmo zangada comigo. Sabias que ela tem um gangue? Já houve algumas ameaças."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:61
translate portuguese u20a_09720660:

    # wt "I've done everything I could to keep her from doing anything drastic."
    wt "Fiz tudo o que pude para a impedir de fazer algo drástico."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:65
translate portuguese u20a_a7898338:

    # wt "Kendra has been really upset with me."
    wt "A Kendra tem estado muito chateada comigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:66
translate portuguese u20a_2c6742f7:

    # wt "She hasn't told the police yet, but I think she would soon."
    wt "Ela ainda não contou à polícia, mas acho que o fará em breve."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:67
translate portuguese u20a_1baaa415:

    # wt "She'll be very happy to see you back home."
    wt "Ela vai ficar muito feliz por te ver de volta a casa."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:71
translate portuguese u20a_009b3a35:

    # wt "Adrian has been asking every day for me to send her in after you."
    wt "A Adrian tem-me pedido todos os dias para a mandar atrás de ti."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:72
translate portuguese u20a_4a9286c6:

    # wt "I might have too. Although, it seems like an endless chain at this point. I send you after your father, then her after you. Who would I have to send after her?"
    wt "Talvez tenha de o fazer. Embora, nesta altura, pareça uma cadeia sem fim. Mando-te atrás do teu pai, depois mando-a atrás de ti. Quem teria de mandar atrás dela?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:76
translate portuguese u20a_85722b6f:

    # wt "Your friend Nora has been quite a handful. She's very angry with me."
    wt "A tua amiga Nora tem dado muito que fazer. Está muito zangada comigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:77
translate portuguese u20a_29032600:

    # wt "She's threatened with everything from the police and lawsuits to physical harm."
    wt "Ameaçou-me com tudo, desde a polícia e processos judiciais até agressão física."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:78
translate portuguese u20a_ad9edb7c:

    # wt "So far I've been able to keep her from doing anything drastic, but I'm really glad you're back. Things could have gotten really bad."
    wt "Até agora, tenho conseguido impedi-la de fazer algo drástico, mas estou muito contente por estares de volta. As coisas podiam ter ficado muito más."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20a.rpy:82
